data.text: #WashingtonFire (#Jamestown, Tuolumne Co) - IC requesting 10 additional engines closest immediate need, the spot fire across Stockton St/Hwy 49 is well established & fire is impacting a structure. The local cameras have gone offline.

entity.name: Cal Fire lifts Red Flag Warnings across the state of California
entity.description: According to Cal Fire, nearly 5,000 firefighters are battling 22 wildfires in California. "Seasonable weather conditions will persist across California today, as Red Flag Warnings have expired," the department announced on Wednesday. On October 27, firefighters responded to 23 new wildfires and all were contained despite Red Flag Warning conditions.

tweets.text: #WashingtonFire (#Jamestown, Tuolumne Co) - IC wants evacuations done for the area behind the fairgrounds, along Stockton St & areas around the waste water treatment plant. AA placing no-divert on tankers due to life safety. https://t.co/WvAS5cygeo
